<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Recupero — Recover Stolen Crypto</title>
<style>
  /* Mobile-first intake form. Designed to be submittable on a phone
     within 90 seconds of landing — victims often hit this URL minutes
     after realizing they've been drained, on whatever device is in
     their hand. */
  :root {
    --ink: #0A0A0A;
    --ink-soft: #1F2937;
    --ink-muted: #4B5563;
    --ink-quiet: #6B7280;
    --paper: #FFFFFF;
    --paper-tint: #FAFAFA;
    --rule: #E5E7EB;
    --gold: #A88B5C;
    --error: #B91C1C;
    --error-bg: #FEF2F2;
    --primary: #1E3A8A;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
      "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    background: var(--paper-tint); color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 22px 80px;
  }
  .brand {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-quiet);
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0 0 14px; color: var(--ink);
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 24px;
  }
  form {
    background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .field { margin: 0 0 18px; }
  .field:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  label {
    display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .hint {
    display: block; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-quiet);
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  input[type="text"], input[type="email"], input[type="date"],
  select, textarea {
    width: 100%; padding: 10px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule); border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 15px; font-family: inherit;
    background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink);
  }
  input[type="text"].mono, textarea.mono {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  textarea { min-height: 100px; resize: vertical; }
  .button-row {
    margin-top: 26px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
  }
  button.primary {
    background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border: none;
    padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
    width: 100%;
  }
  button.primary:hover { background: #1A337A; }
  .price-line {
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-quiet); text-align: center;
  }
  .error-banner {
    background: var(--error-bg); border-left: 3px solid var(--error);
    padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 0 0 22px;
    color: var(--error);
  }
  .error-banner strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .small { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-quiet); }
  hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); margin: 28px 0; }
  .reassurance {
    background: var(--paper-tint); padding: 18px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px; margin: 28px 0;
  }
  .reassurance h3 {
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-quiet); margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .reassurance li { margin: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; }

  /* v0.32 Tier-0 gap #2 — recovery-rate disclosure block.
     Visually distinct (warm border, slight tint) so the customer
     cannot miss it; lives ABOVE the checkout button so they read
     the number before they reach for the credit card. */
  .recovery-disclosure {
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    background: #FFFBF2;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .recovery-disclosure h3 {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.10em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .recovery-disclosure .rate-line {
    font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .recovery-disclosure .rate-detail {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .recovery-disclosure .ack-row {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
    padding: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .recovery-disclosure .ack-row input[type="checkbox"] {
    margin-top: 3px; flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 18px; height: 18px;
  }
  .recovery-disclosure .ack-row label {
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0; cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <p class="brand">Recupero · Investigation Services</p>
  <h1>Crypto stolen? Let's trace it.</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    Submit your wallet address and a brief description of what
    happened. Within 24 hours of payment we will trace your funds
    on-chain, identify where they currently sit, and tell you
    exactly which exchanges or token issuers we can ask to freeze
    them — and what your realistic recovery probability is.
  </p>

  {% if error %}
  <div class="error-banner">
    <strong>{{ error.field | replace('_', ' ') | title }}</strong>
    {{ error.detail }}
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <form method="POST" action="/v1/intake" autocomplete="on">
    <div class="field">
      <label for="client_name">Your full legal name</label>
      <span class="hint">Required for the engagement letter if you proceed.</span>
      <input type="text" id="client_name" name="client_name"
             value="{{ form.client_name or '' }}"
             required maxlength="200" autocomplete="name">
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label for="client_email">Email address</label>
      <span class="hint">We'll send your case status and updates here.</span>
      <input type="email" id="client_email" name="client_email"
             value="{{ form.client_email or '' }}"
             required maxlength="320" autocomplete="email">
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label for="chain">Blockchain</label>
      <span class="hint">Which chain were the funds on when they were stolen?</span>
      <select id="chain" name="chain" required>
        <option value="">— select —</option>
        <option value="ethereum"{% if form.chain == 'ethereum' %} selected{% endif %}>Ethereum</option>
        <option value="arbitrum"{% if form.chain == 'arbitrum' %} selected{% endif %}>Arbitrum</option>
        <option value="base"{% if form.chain == 'base' %} selected{% endif %}>Base</option>
        <option value="polygon"{% if form.chain == 'polygon' %} selected{% endif %}>Polygon</option>
        <option value="bsc"{% if form.chain == 'bsc' %} selected{% endif %}>BNB Chain</option>
        <option value="solana"{% if form.chain == 'solana' %} selected{% endif %}>Solana</option>
        <option value="tron"{% if form.chain == 'tron' %} selected{% endif %}>Tron</option>
        <option value="bitcoin"{% if form.chain == 'bitcoin' %} selected{% endif %}>Bitcoin</option>
        <option value="hyperliquid"{% if form.chain == 'hyperliquid' %} selected{% endif %}>Hyperliquid</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label for="seed_address">Your wallet address</label>
      <span class="hint">The wallet that was drained. Copy-paste the full address.</span>
      <input type="text" id="seed_address" name="seed_address"
             class="mono"
             value="{{ form.seed_address or '' }}"
             required maxlength="80" autocomplete="off"
             placeholder="0x… or bc1… or T… etc.">
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label for="incident_date">Date of theft</label>
      <span class="hint">Approximate is OK if you're not sure.</span>
      <input type="date" id="incident_date" name="incident_date"
             value="{{ form.incident_date or '' }}"
             required>
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label for="country">Your country (optional)</label>
      <span class="hint">Helps us route to the right law-enforcement channel.</span>
      <input type="text" id="country" name="country"
             value="{{ form.country or '' }}"
             maxlength="100" autocomplete="country-name">
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label for="description">What happened?</label>
      <span class="hint">One or two sentences. We'll ask more if needed.</span>
      <textarea id="description" name="description"
                required maxlength="2000"
                placeholder="e.g. Phishing site drained my wallet on May 5; I signed what I thought was a routine swap…">{{ form.description or '' }}</textarea>
    </div>

    {# v0.32 Tier-0 gap #2 — honest recovery-rate disclosure.
       Rendered ABOVE the checkout button so the customer reads
       the number before they reach for the credit card. The
       checkbox is HTML5-required AND server-side-validated in
       the POST handler. #}
    {% if recovery_stats %}
    <div class="recovery-disclosure">
      <h3>Honest recovery-rate disclosure</h3>
      {% if recovery_stats.is_our_data %}
        <p class="rate-line">
          We recover stolen funds for
          <strong>{{ "%.0f"|format(recovery_stats.full_recovery_rate * 100) }}%</strong>
          (95% CI:
          {{ "%.0f"|format(recovery_stats.full_recovery_rate_ci_low * 100) }}%–{{ "%.0f"|format(recovery_stats.full_recovery_rate_ci_high * 100) }}%)
          of cases.
        </p>
        <p class="rate-detail">
          Based on our last {{ recovery_stats.sample_size }} closed cases
          ({{ recovery_stats.n_full_recovery }} full recoveries,
          {{ recovery_stats.n_partial_recovery }} partial freezes,
          {{ recovery_stats.n_zero_recovery }} zero recoveries).
          {% if recovery_stats.median_recovery_usd %}
          Median recovery on wins: ${{ "{:,.0f}".format(recovery_stats.median_recovery_usd) }}.
          {% endif %}
        </p>
      {% else %}
        <p class="rate-line">
          The crypto-recovery industry baseline is approximately
          <strong>{{ "%.0f"|format(recovery_stats.full_recovery_rate * 100) }}% full-recovery</strong>
          and ~7% partial-recovery
          <span class="small">(Chainalysis 2024)</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="rate-detail">
          We have {{ recovery_stats.sample_size }} closed case{% if recovery_stats.sample_size != 1 %}s{% endif %} of our own;
          we will publish our own rate once we reach 30+ closed cases.
        </p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="ack-row">
        <input type="checkbox" id="acknowledge_disclosure"
               name="acknowledge_disclosure" value="yes" required
               {% if form.acknowledge_disclosure == 'yes' %}checked{% endif %}>
        <label for="acknowledge_disclosure">
          I understand that paying for this diagnostic does
          <strong>NOT</strong> guarantee recovery of my funds.
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="button-row">
      <button type="submit" class="primary">
        Continue to payment ($499)
      </button>
      <p class="price-line">
        $499 forensic diagnostic · refundable if no recoverable
        funds identified.
      </p>
    </div>
  </form>

  <div class="reassurance">
    <h3>What you get for $499</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Full on-chain forensic trace of where your funds went</li>
      <li>Identified destinations: which exchanges or token issuers hold them now</li>
      <li>Recovery probability score with per-issuer breakdown</li>
      <li>If recoverable, an engagement option to send formal freeze requests on your behalf</li>
      <li>If not recoverable, a full refund and an honest reason why</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <p class="small">
    Recupero is an investigation service. We are not a law firm
    and we do not provide legal advice. If your case requires
    legal representation we will refer you to a cooperating attorney.
    Submitting this form does not create an attorney-client
    relationship and does not guarantee any specific outcome.
  </p>

</div>
</body>
</html>
